&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    大堰川の浅瀬で餌を探すアオサギ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Birds" /><summary type="html">A gray heron looks for food in the shallow water of the Oi (Katsura) River. 大堰川の浅瀬で餌を探すアオサギ。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05600.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05600.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Afternoon in Arashiyama・嵐山の午後</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220309/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Afternoon in Arashiyama・嵐山の午後" /><published>2022-03-09T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-09T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220309/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
