&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    渡月橋と西京都の山々。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Togetsu-kyo Bridge and the mountains of western Kyoto. 渡月橋と西京都の山々。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_APC_4222-hdr.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_APC_4222-hdr.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pray for Peace・平和を祈る</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220307/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pray for Peace・平和を祈る" /><published>2022-03-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ukraine</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220307/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
